  <div class="unity-box">🎮 <strong>Unity Inspector note:</strong> Properties do NOT appear in the Inspector — only fields do. Use <code>[SerializeField] private float speed;</code> for Inspector-editable values, and properties for computed or protected access from code.</div>
</div>

