}

<span class="cm">// ── Layer Mask — only hit specific layers ──</span>
<span class="kw">public</span> <span class="ty">LayerMask</span> enemyLayer;
<span class="kw">if</span> (<span class="uk">Physics</span>.<span class="fn">Raycast</span>(ray, <span class="kw">out</span> hit, <span class="num">100f</span>, enemyLayer))
{
    <span class="cm">// Only enemies on that layer are detected</span>
}</pre>
  <div class="unity-box">🎮 <strong>Layer Masks</strong> — assign objects to layers in the Inspector, then use a LayerMask to filter raycasts. Avoids hitting the player's own collider or UI elements. Expose the LayerMask as a public field and set it in the Inspector.</div>
