['audioSource','PlayOneShot','Range','PlayOneShot','coinClip','1f'])}
${CHALLENGES([
  "Build a simple audio manager with play/stop/pause/resume methods and expose volume control.",
  "Create footstep sounds that play every 0.4 seconds while the player is moving (use a coroutine).",
  "Add music that transitions between combat music and exploration music based on enemy proximity.",
  "Build a sound pool: pre-create 5 AudioSources so rapid sounds (gunshots) can overlap without clipping.",
