    anim.${blank('SetTrigger',11)}(<span class="str">"Jump"</span>);

<span class="cm">// Persistent bool — true while in air</span>
anim.${blank('SetBool',8)}(<span class="str">"IsGrounded"</span>, ${blank('IsGrounded',11)}());`,
['Animator','GetComponent','magnitude','SetFloat','SetTrigger','SetBool','IsGrounded'])}

${CHALLENGES([
  "Record a simple idle animation for a cube — make it pulse up and down 0.2 units using Transform.position keyframes.",
  "Create a state machine with Idle and Walk states. Add a float Speed parameter. Wire transitions: Idle→Walk when Speed > 0.1, Walk→Idle when Speed < 0.1.",
